OL,3,CHotter than holiday hotspots: UK
OL,4,Cspring surge sees temperatures soar
OL,6,FRising temperatures across across the
OL,7,FUK are set to give the nation a mood
OL,8,Fboost as many places are on track to
OL,9,Frecord their warmest day of the year
OL,10,Fso far.
OL,12,FWhere will be warmest and how warm
OL,13,Fwill it get?
OL,15,FTemperatures will be boosted above -
OL,16,Fand for some well above - the seasonal
OL,17,Faverage right across the UK on
OL,18,FWednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
