OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773857158
OL,3,CHotter than holiday hotspots: UK
OL,4,Cspring surge sees temperatures soar
OL,6,FThe warmest places are likely to be
OL,7,Facross the Cardigan Bay area in mid
OL,8,Fwest Wales, the west coast and also
OL,9,Fwestern and northwestern England.
OL,11,FIn the best of the sunshine,
OL,12,Ftemperatures could reach 20-21C!
OL,14,FWhy is this happening?
OL,16,FThe boost in temperatures is down to
OL,17,Fhigh pressure stretching in from the
OL,18,Feast, holding clouds and rain-bearing
OL,19,FAtlantic fronts at bay, and allowing
OL,20,Flots of sunshine to develop.
OL,26,@tD@_OX
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
