OL,3,CHotter than holiday hotspots: UK
OL,4,Cspring surge sees temperatures soar
OL,6,FA warm spell in mid March is not
OL,7,Fterribly unusual; early spring sees
OL,8,Fhuge temperature swings which slowly
OL,9,Fstart to settle down as we move
OL,10,Fthrough the season.
OL,12,FHaving said that, blue skies and
OL,13,Ftemperatures soaring 10-12C above the
OL,14,Fseasonal average is uncommon enough to
OL,15,Fbe sure that you make the most of it!
OL,17,FHow long will it last?
OL,19,FThe warmest temperatures will almost
OL,20,Fcertainly be today.
OL,26,@uD@[OX
