OL,3,CHotter than holiday hotspots: UK
OL,4,Cspring surge sees temperatures soar
OL,6,FThroughout the rest of the week and
OL,7,Finto the weekend, winds will start to
OL,8,Fback more northeasterly which will
OL,9,Fdrag in less mild air.
OL,11,FStill plenty of lovely weather to be
OL,12,Fhad for most of us though but if it's
OL,13,Fthe warm temperatures that you're
OL,14,Fcraving, today is the day!
