OL,3,CHotter than holiday hotspots: UK
OL,4,Cspring surge sees temperatures soar
OL,6,FHow does the UK warmth compare to
OL,7,Fclassic Mediterranean destinations?
OL,9,FThis is always a fun exercise when the
OL,10,FUK weather is lovely!
OL,12,FHere is what I like to call the 'smug
OL,13,Flist' - all the places that will be
OL,14,Fless warm our UK max tomorrow, and
OL,15,Ftheir maximum temperatures.
OL,17,FSantorini, Greece - 17C
OL,19,FRome, Italy - 15C
OL,21,FMadrid, Spain - 16C
